.TH RPISTAT "1" "2022" "rpistat" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
rpistat \- Web-Service to collect system usage statistics
.SH DESCRIPTION
Web-Service to collect system usage statistics
.SS "Usage:"
.IP
rpistat [flags]
rpistat [command]
.SS "Available Commands:"
.TP
version
print this program version
